        <h1 class="article__title" itemprop="headline">Adelaide carbon neutral plan launched</h1>

    </header>

    <div class="article__introduction" itemprop="about"><p>The next step to make Adelaide the world’s first carbon neutral city was taken yesterday, with the launch of the Carbon Neutral Adelaide Action Plan 2016-2021.</p></div>

    <figure class="article__image" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject">

